Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.53,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:25.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有星光的迷宫里挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:30.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:36.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受灵魂的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:41.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙正在呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:47.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负伤痕 知晓孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:52.50,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白了羁绊的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:55.36,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除阴翳眼眸中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.99,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安和困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:04.50,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:08.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士们 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:14.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果背负的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够称为爱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:19.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士们相互支持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化为风的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:26.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新的Ω神话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:31.40,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:21.00,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超必杀 幻影之爪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的埃吉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太过轻视黄金圣斗士 天秤座玄武了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金圣衣居然如此牢固？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟让我蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许珀里翁大人的圣剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要借我使用么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是圣剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小宇宙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从剑里散发出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这散发出伟大的小宇宙的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名为 天地崩灭斩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自神话时代起就流传下来的众神的圣剑之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此剑一挥便可崩天裂地 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃是灭绝一切的破坏之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一级刻斗士 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四天王许珀里翁大人的佩剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说许珀里翁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许珀里翁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我埃吉尔将感恩戴德地使用天地崩灭斩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任你剑 箭 还是火枪 尽管来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为掌管均衡与和谐的黄金圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我天秤座玄武是不会被打败的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也已经发觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这其中压倒一切的攻击性的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何等强大而不祥的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵型不要乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小宇宙好强大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去Palaestra会被毁灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被这把剑散发出的和阿普斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 比那更强大的小宇宙所摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地崩灭斩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭违抗帕拉斯大人的圣斗士们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武的死斗！圣剑对天秤之剑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙居然可以燃烧到这等地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁天灭地之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一击致命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是许珀里翁大人的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可劈斩一切的破坏之剑 天地崩灭斩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹杀圣斗士 只凭一把剑就足够了吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许珀里翁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就无需我出场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金圣斗士之流 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我伟大的圣剑面前 将如尘埃般灰飞烟灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座黄金圣斗士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想让你也看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这天地崩灭斩之下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士悉数横死的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马座
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再让你向前一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可爱的学弟学妹们都在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能让你通过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是弑神并击败黄金的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能打败身为二级刻斗士的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需要借助一级刻斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四天王许珀里翁大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一级…刻斗士？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是相当于圣斗士中的黄金圣斗士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一级的力量可以轻松凌驾于黄金圣斗士之上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻斗士的水准和你们这些圣斗士可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看天秤座的尸身 就清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁的尸身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 吃了天地崩灭斩的攻击还…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看黄金圣衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是有着圆盾的天秤座圣衣 怎可能会被击破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你们会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你们出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事 这家伙是我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫埃吉尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着你那天地崩灭斩的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我不会让你渡过此桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要渡过的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.66,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三途河，冥界河名，相传为生死分界，在此前的圣斗士篇章中有所涉及
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三途河！     
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥什么的根本无须渡过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来告诉你吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地崩灭斩的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此剑将斩断和破碎时空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拭目以待吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地崩灭斩是可以斩断时间逻辑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的时间啊 停止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时光毁灭（Chrono Destruction）！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的小宇宙消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是停止了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么 埃吉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我破坏了所有事物的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然 你这家伙似乎被黄金圣衣保护了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这些家伙的时间已经被这把剑夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾呢 你没能保护Palaestra
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很微弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能动 却还拥有意识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为受到从圣衣石中新生的圣衣的保护吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这家伙怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为受到了天马座的保护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是潜在的小宇宙特别强大？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒夺走时间的刻斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能恢复原状了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是简单易懂的规则呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你能打倒我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一招就让你亲身体验这把剑的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会如你所愿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座的圣衣中包括圆盾在内 有六种武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:11:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拐 双节棍 三节棍 枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及天秤之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士禁止使用武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非雅典娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或天秤座圣斗士下达许可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能使用这武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光环绕的天秤圣衣之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾师童虎 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所传授给我的天秤座武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:48.09,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激战！圣剑与天秤之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接我一剑吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护雅典娜的黄金圣斗士 天秤之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那破玩意在这天地崩灭斩面前和把钝刀无异
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我怎么斩断它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能接住这天地崩灭斩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看这个能粉碎星辰的天秤之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 看样子双剑相交时所释放出的巨大小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算剑能承受 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金圣衣也不能完全抵御天地崩灭斩的冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身体已经受到了损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经毫无胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在许珀里翁大人的面前吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾师童虎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常被您说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我是个没有毅力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里倒下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对师父也好 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对年轻的圣斗士也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都无法做出榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为何要站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了将师父的遗志传递给年轻的圣斗士们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少装帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾师童虎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我的师兄紫龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像他们为了同伴拼上性命一次次站起来那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算牺牲性命 我也要保护这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 在这天地崩灭斩面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的圣斗士都将灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就给你最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真是不像样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站着就升天了么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还扬言说要保护青铜圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就只剩粉碎剩下的圣斗士了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选择了愚蠢地白白送死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔 拔不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 你挨了这天地崩灭斩还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我玄武不会白死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把剑可不是为了打败你而出鞘的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没把你放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的对手从一开始 便是位于这把剑另一端的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要毁掉这把剑 大家就能复原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我这天秤座之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了毁掉天地崩灭斩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才用自己的身体接住了剑不成？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少以我的性命作交换 摧毁这把剑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的圣斗士们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承我之灵魂 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭强大的邪恶势力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾师童虎的遗志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我继承了天秤座圣衣一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士在新的时代 应建立起自己的意志并将它托付给下一代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许珀里翁 你的剑就由我玄武收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庐山升天霸！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是无法破坏它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的小宇宙正在恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃吉尔 你手持吾剑应战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还落得这般田地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能除掉一名黄金圣斗士 结果也算差强人意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么回去 肯定会被问罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让许珀里翁大人借与我的剑出现伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许珀里翁大人定会盛怒不已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会饶了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能干掉他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弑神的光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能奉上这小子的首级！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武 你的意志 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经确确实实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确确实实地感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙君！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打爆他！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙的小宇宙燃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…这…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚…虚张声势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我这招 超必杀 幻影之爪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马流星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃吉尔大人被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟能打倒他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大惊小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我的守护星座的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本说过有时间要与你好好交谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我食言了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的战斗和小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经向我诉说了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从您身上受益良多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深得您之教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 我的师父就是 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲紫龙和天秤座玄武您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信你自己的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你们 一定能够觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的话 一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武先生——！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄武 你的死一定会激起轩然大波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小宇宙一定能够让圣斗士们行动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤座的黄金圣斗士玄武之死所带来的冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛是要更进一步紧逼陷入不安中的圣斗士们而出现的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手座的星矢 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及女神雅典娜 终于降临战场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的反击从现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 圣斗士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢，出阵！雅典娜的决意！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
